strings: <voice_0x01000E38><se_high>Red: What are you doin' showin' your ugly face round here again!? I said I've got nothin' more to say to ya.

<voice_0x01000E39><se_high>Red: So? What is it this time, eh?
Don't tell me you've come to check on me health!
<voice_0x01000E3A><se_low>Yangus: No, we was just passin'. The guv's managed to get 'old of this ship, right, so...

<voice_0x01000E3B><se_high>Red: So yer 'ere to show off? Do me a lemon!
I've got me own ship, so you can save yer breath.

<voice_0x01000E3C><se_high>Red: I'd show it to yer if I could, but I can't right now. Shame, cos she's a quality vessel.
The Classy Lady, she's called.

<voice_0x01000E3D><se_low>Yangus: ...Nah, I weren't tryin' to show off or nuffin'!
Gordon Bennett, 'ow did we end up gettin' into all this!
